Nollywood veteran actor, Richard Mofe Damijo, has shared a photo he took 20 years ago with his colleague, Sola Sobowale, and Nigerian comedian, Olateju Oyelakin aka Teju Babyface. The actor shared the picture via his Instagram account on Thursday. ALSO READ: Actress Eniola Badmus remembers late mother after 19 years In the caption, he wrote, “How time flies” na this picture be that so, taken over 20 years ago shuuu. My dearest aburo #solasobowale & see as #tejubabyfaceoyelakin resemble small pikin. “ 